As of the [[2020 United States census|2020 census]],<ref>{{cite web |title=Desoto Acres CDP, Florida |url=https://data.census.gov/profile?g=160XX00US1217273 |publisher=United States Census Bureau |access-date=13 April 2023}}</ref> Desoto Acres had a population of 720 with a total of 296 households. The median household income was $68,986. 30.3% of the population 25 years and older had a bachelor's degree or higher. The CDP had an employment rate of 73.1%. 10.9% of the population lived without healthcare coverage.

